{"tid":1548113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角持刀中坑被市民追截　後稱遇襲受傷","createTime":"2019-09-07T02:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T02:45:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e96dcb58430f9d5b6e608df1e51f408d7adf3278","tid":1548113,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190907/s00001/5dab2093b0435299f4d239511c4516f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190907%2Fs00001%2F5dab2093b0435299f4d239511c4516f6.jpg&h=3cc6b2c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚（6日）近11時，一名穿紅色上衣的中年漢在旺角新填地街及奶路臣街交界，不斷揮動手上的菜刀及鐵通，其女友在場制止期間受傷，一批市民追截中年漢，並向中年漢投擲垃圾桶、雨傘等物件，市民追至廣東道1033號一幢唐樓，發現2樓一個單位外地面有血迹，遂破壞單位大門；現場附近後巷遺下一把疑中年漢事發時手持的菜刀。<br />\n<br />\n59歲中年漢臉及手受傷，其42歲女友則眼及手受傷，送往廣華醫院治理。警方經調查後則表示，中年漢與其女友當時在新填地街及奶路臣街交界因瑣事爭執，其後約3名男子跟隨他們至廣東道1033號，並懷疑以硬物襲擊及毀壞2樓單位的大門。案件暫列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，交由旺角警區刑事調查隊第一隊跟進調查，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190907/s00001/5dc6eac0e1b8856dd12224d3b66ee575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190907%2Fs00001%2F5dc6eac0e1b8856dd12224d3b66ee575.jpg&h=346e395d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190907/s00001/1567820718745/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E6%8C%81%E5%88%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E8%A2%AB%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%BF%BD%E6%88%AA-%E5%BE%8C%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190907%2Fs00001%2F1567820718745%2F%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%2588%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%2588%25AA-%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=5ef1aac7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190907%2Fs00001%2F1567820718745%2F%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%2588%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%2588%25AA-%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7&h=6a1b0ebf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190907/s00001/1567820718745/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E6%8C%81%E5%88%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E8%A2%AB%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%BF%BD%E6%88%AA-%E5%BE%8C%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7</a>"},{"pid":"25553ba7b0b91cc24c646fbf66aa62da987176d9","tid":1548113,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:18:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbd8bd74ca088f0073b0d9ed3441e01fb069d994","tid":1548113,"uid":205199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:19:19.000Z","msg":"佢道門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee77d3e0652df531fa390d25ea297fc63ea1b13","tid":1548113,"uid":233651,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fbd8bd74ca088f0073b0d9ed3441e01fb069d994","tid":1548113,"uid":205199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:19:19.000Z","msg":"佢道門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:22:27.000Z","msg":"FC左係打風吹爛"},{"pid":"f72d7a316a1a8109dec361